--
-- Given  h : Sp(BвҲһ) = BoolHom BвҲһ BoolBR, extract the binary sequence
--   ОұвӮҷ = h(gвҲһ n).
-- The relations  gвҲһ m В·вҲһ gвҲһ n = 0  for m вү  n  force  Оұ  to hit true
