--
-- Recall from the tex (Theorem LLPO, lines 541вҖ“595):
--
--   For all Оұ : NвҲһ,
--     (вҲҖ k. Оұ_{2k} = 0) вҲЁ (вҲҖ k. Оұ_{2k+1} = 0)
--
-- The proof constructs a map  f : BвҲһ вҶ’ BвҲһ Г— BвҲһ  and shows it is injective.
-- By the axiom SurjectionsAreFormalSurjections, the induced map
--   Sp(f) : Sp(BвҲһ Г— BвҲһ) вҶ’ Sp(BвҲһ)
